	   <tr><td colspan=2>I agree with everything Khift has said here.&nbsp;&nbsp;I do however think that the Warmaster's Ribcage, dropped by a Possessed Warmaster (5th wave ring of fire), also comes close to this BP (+50AC +15Str +15Sta +15Agi +15Dex +15Wis +15Int +15Cha +5vsMg +5vsFire +5vsCold +5vsPos +5vsDis +100HP +100Mana +10.00 Wt), but mainly for Paladins and Shadowknights.  This is due to the +15 Int/Wis, +100 Mana and the lighter weight. <br><br>Theodus<br>49 Dwarf Paladin <br>Fennin Ro by way of Tallon Zek<br><br><br><em id=fs8>Edited, Wed Sep 25 10:28:28 2002</em><br>&nbsp;<br>Theo"X"<br>Tallon Zek & Fennin Ro</td></tr>
